{
  "stem": "812.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Every day, without fail, we were asked to stand on appell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "That meant that we were all sent out into a large field, and we were lined up five in a row, and there we were counted.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "And everyone had to be accounted for before we were allowed to leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "This was no matter what the weather, no matter how warm or how cold, how rainy or how cold, how much snow or ice there was.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "We had to stand at attention and until everyone was accounted for.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "The Germans did their utmost to break us mentally, physically, and emotionally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "And it-- it was not unusual for people to try to escape, even though they knew very well that it was next to impossible to succeed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we would realize their failure at the attempt when we saw their bodies electrocuted against the wires.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I, personally, spent my days with a game of superstition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] would say to myself, if I were to find-- I would constantly search, and I would search for four pebbles, four perfect pebbles approximately the same size and shape.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "And I said to myself, if I find those four pebbles, that that-- that would mean that my father, my mother, my brother, and I would survive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "It was a torturous pastime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "It was a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a game that I-- I played, I needed to play, because it gave me some distant hope, some-- something to hold onto.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "And this went on daily.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "And whenever I would start to search for my pebbles, I would make it my business, I would-- to find that fourth pebble.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
